用这个模板帮我写一个发表论文清单的模板

下面给你一个可直接复用的“发表论文清单”LaTeX 模板（沿用你给的 IEEEtran onecolumn + 1.5 倍行距风格）。你只需要把 `\PaperEntry{...}` 里的内容替换成你的论文信息即可。

```latex
\documentclass[10pt,journal,onecolumn,final]{IEEEtran}

\usepackage{amssymb}
\usepackage{cite}
\ifCLASSINFOpdf
\usepackage{colortbl}
\usepackage{bm}
\usepackage{float}
\usepackage[section]{placeins}
\usepackage[pdftex]{graphicx}
\graphicspath{{../pdf/}{../jpeg/}}
\DeclareGraphicsExtensions{.pdf,.jpeg,.png}
\else
\fi

\usepackage{amsmath}
\usepackage{algorithm}
\usepackage{algorithmic}
\usepackage{multirow}
\usepackage{wrapfig}
\usepackage{array}
\usepackage{color}
\usepackage{framed}
\usepackage{stfloats}
\usepackage{caption}
\usepackage{url}
\usepackage[dvipsnames]{xcolor}
\usepackage{pdfpages}
\usepackage{hyperref}
\usepackage{cleveref}
\usepackage{booktabs}
\usepackage{setspace}
\usepackage{lmodern}
\setstretch{1.5}

% ---------------------------
% Paper list utilities
% ---------------------------
\newcommand{\Heading}[1]{%
  \vspace{6pt}\noindent{\large\bfseries #1}\par\vspace{2pt}\hrule\vspace{6pt}
}

% Fields:
% 1 Title
% 2 Authors (bold your name if needed)
% 3 Venue (conference/journal)
% 4 Status (Accepted/Published/Under Review/Preprint)
% 5 Year
% 6 Links (PDF/Code/Project) - can be empty
\newcommand{\PaperEntry}[6]{%
  \noindent\textbf{#1}\par
  \noindent #2\par
  \noindent \textit{#3} \hfill \textbf{#4} (#5)\par
  \if\relax\detokenize{#6}\relax
  \vspace{6pt}
  \else
  \noindent \textcolor{MidnightBlue}{#6}\par\vspace{6pt}
  \fi
}

\begin{document}
\clearpage

\noindent
{\LARGE\bfseries Publication List}\\[6pt]
\noindent
Name: \textbf{YOUR NAME} \\
Affiliation: YOUR AFFILIATION \\
Last updated: \today

\vspace{10pt}

% ---------------------------
% Summary (optional)
% ---------------------------
\Heading{Summary}
\noindent
Total papers: \textbf{11} \\
First / co-first author: \textbf{6} \\
Accepted by top-tier venues (e.g., CVPR/NeurIPS/ICLR/ICCV): \textbf{7}

% ---------------------------
% Sections
% ---------------------------
\Heading{Peer-reviewed Conference Papers}
\PaperEntry
{Paper Title A}
{\textbf{Your Name}, Coauthor1, Coauthor2}
{CVPR}
{Accepted}
{2025}
{\href{https://arxiv.org/abs/xxxx.xxxxx}{arXiv} \quad|\quad
 \href{https://github.com/xxx/xxx}{Code}}

\PaperEntry
{Paper Title B}
{Coauthor1, \textbf{Your Name}, Coauthor2}
{NeurIPS}
{Published}
{2024}
{\href{https://openreview.net/forum?id=XXXX}{OpenReview}}

\Heading{Peer-reviewed Journal Articles}
\PaperEntry
{Paper Title C}
{\textbf{Your Name}, Coauthor1, Coauthor2}
{IEEE Transactions on Pattern Analysis and Machine Intelligence (TPAMI)}
{Under Review}
{2026}
{}

\Heading{Preprints / Workshop Papers (Optional)}
\PaperEntry
{Paper Title D}
{\textbf{Your Name}, Coauthor1}
{arXiv}
{Preprint}
{2023}
{\href{https://arxiv.org/abs/xxxx.xxxxx}{arXiv}}

% ---------------------------
% Notes (optional)
% ---------------------------
\Heading{Notes}
\begin{itemize}
  \item \textbf{Co-first author}: authors contributed equally.
  \item Your name is \textbf{bolded}.
\end{itemize}

\end{document}
```

如果你把你的 11 篇论文的标题/作者/会议期刊/状态/年份/链接发我（哪怕是表格或 BibTeX），我可以帮你自动整理成上述 `\PaperEntry{}` 格式，并按“已接收顶会/期刊、在投、预印本”等分组排版。
